# Deploy After Logo/Asset Update

When updating partner logos (`assets/partners/*`) or Pekan logos (`assets/pekan*.png`):

1. **Always deploy** after the update: add, commit, and push to `origin main`
2. Use a clear commit message, e.g.: `Update logo: [company name]` or `Update partner logos: [list]`
3. GitHub Pages will auto-deploy from the main branch

Commands:
```bash
git add assets/partners/ assets/
git commit -m "Update logo: [company]"
git push origin main
```
